<br>
His last visions.....were filled with terror.<br>
<br>
In a brief moment of panic he grasps for anything to help him to his feet.  He stumbles and manages to get to one knee.  He feels a small hand on his back.<br>
<br>
&quot;May Tunare comfort thee...&quot;, Says a female voice in the bell like tone of High Elvish.  Aryllyian feels the wave of healing come over him, his vision clears, and he is able to focus clearly on the divine being near him.<br>
<br>
It is the face of Seyah.  He coughs and tries to force a smile, but he is still very weak.  He wants to thank her.<br>
<br>
&quot;I know, Lord Aryllyian, shhhhh...now...save yer strength.&quot; says Seyah calmly.    <br>
